# CONCERT TICKET BOOKING SYSTEM - Requirement Clarification & Discussion
## Amazon SDE2 LLD Interview Prep

---

## 🎯 Problem Statement
Design a **Concert Ticket Booking System** (like BookMyShow, Ticketmaster) that allows users to browse concerts, select seats, and book tickets with proper handling of seat availability and concurrent booking attempts.

