## 🗣️ Clarifying Questions & Answers

### 1. WHO — Actors

**Q: Who are the different users of this system?**

**A:**
| Actor | Capabilities |
|-------|-------------|
| **Customer** | Browse concerts, select seats, book tickets, cancel bookings |
| **Admin** | Create/edit concerts, add venues, view reports |

For this interview, focus on **Customer** operations. Admin is simple CRUD.

---

### 2. WHAT — Core Entities

**Q: What are the main entities and their types?**

**A:**

**Venue:**
- Physical location where concerts happen
- Has name, address, sections
- One venue can host many concerts

**Concert:**
- An event at a venue on a specific date
- Has artist name, date/time, venue reference
- Has many seats (via venue layout)

**Seat:**
- Individual bookable unit
- Has row, seat number, section
- Three categories:

| Category | Price | Description |
|----------|-------|-------------|
| **VIP** | ₹5000 | Front rows, close to stage |
| **PREMIUM** | ₹2000 | Middle sections |
| **REGULAR** | ₹500 | Back/side sections |

**Booking:**
- Links user to seats for a concert
- Can include 1-10 seats
- Has status (PENDING, CONFIRMED, CANCELLED)

